\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n 1 tu\u1ea7n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch l\u1ea1i \u0111ang \u1edf v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u0103ng hoa khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 8 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (th\u1eafng 5).\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/9/dortmund.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1edfi v\u1eady, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Marco Reus nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi Dortmund v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t h\u1ed3n trong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. H\u01a1n 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Die Borussen b\u1ebf t\u1eafc ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh trong khi Stuttgart nhi\u1ec1u phen khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u00f3t tim v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, may m\u1eafn l\u1ea1i m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 38, Pulisic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, b\u00f3ng \u0111i c\u1ea7u \u00e2u v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cu\u1ed9n th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Stuttgart. 1-0 cho Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pulisic c\u0169ng \u201cm\u1eaft tr\u00f2n m\u1eaft d\u1eb9t\u201d v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u201ctr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng\u201d c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dortmund tr\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Ph\u00fat 41, Sahin c\u00f3 pha b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft cho Reus tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng b\u1eaft v\u00f4-l\u00ea \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c. 1-0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u1edf ph\u00fat 48. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c Batshuayi. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 pha l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 v\u1ea9y m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i cho Sahin tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Zieler t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng v\u00e0o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua Dortmund vs Stuttgart 3-0 tuong thuat Bundesliga 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Dortmund vs Stuttgart 3-0 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt Bundesliga 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/180408_224021_432.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Batshuayi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Dortmund</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 59, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an b\u00e0i v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Dortmund. T\u1eeb pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Dahoud, Pulisic \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho Philipp d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh Zieler, n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-0 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf an to\u00e0n, Dortmund gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Stuttgart l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c d\u00e2ng l\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra. Ph\u00fat 72, Pulisic kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u2026 vai c\u1ee7a Zieler sau pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ef1c k\u00ec th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. 13 ph\u00fat sau, Gomez l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m rung chuy\u1ec3n khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m x\u00e0 ngang.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi v\u00e0 3-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Dortmund c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Die Borussen, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn\u2026 35 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn Revierderby v\u1edbi Schalke 04 v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u201cchung k\u1ebft\u201d cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec Bundesliga m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u:<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDortmund: Burki, Piszczek, Toprak, Sokratis, Schmelzer (Toljan, 64\u2019), Sahin, Dahoud, Pulisic, Reus (Sergio Gomez, 87\u2019), Philipp (Sancho, 80\u2019), Batshuayi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nStuttgart: Zieler, Beck, Pavard, Badstuber, Insua, Thommy (Larsen, 57\u2019), Aogo (Ozcan, 68\u2019), Ascacibar (Mangala, 88\u2019), Gentner, Ginczek, Gomez.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"933","checkdouble":"183848"},{"date":"04:17 09/04","title":"HLV Zidane gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-zidane-giai-thich-ly-do-cristiano-ronaldo-bi-thay-ra.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weigh