fy;\">Gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra trong hi\u1ec7p hai, HLV Zinedine Zidane cho bi\u1ebft mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi Los Blancos c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh Madrid kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng d\u00e0nh cho ri\u00eang ai khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Cristiano Ronaldo</span></span> (Real Madrid) m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 53, c\u00f2n Antoine Griezmann (Atletico) ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 4 ph\u00fat sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo bi thay ra trong tran derby Madrid.\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra trong tr\u1eadn derby Madrid.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/hlv-zidane-giai-thich-ly-do-cristiano-ronaldo-bi-thay-ra.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra trong tr\u1eadn derby Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 l\u01b0u t\u00e2m l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra b\u1edfi Karim Benzema \u1edf ph\u00fat 64. Vi\u1ec7c Cr7 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u suy \u0111o\u00e1n, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha hi\u1ebfm khi b\u1ecb thay ra gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 Real Madrid ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane, vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo b\u1ecb thay ra \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y: &quot;\u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 th\u1ebf. \u0110\u00f4i khi anh \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Cristiano v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Cristiano, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y trong su\u1ed1t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 50 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a. S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid v\u1eabn k\u00e9m Atletico kho\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tay-ban-nha/bang-xep-hang-5.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng La Liga</span>. Khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Barca, HLV Zidane c\u00f3 l\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-Madrid.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Real Madrid 1-1 Atletico:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/8/real-1-1-atletico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"932","checkdouble":"183841"},{"date":"04:37 09/04","title":"Sergio Ramos nh\u1eafn Barca: \"Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ec5 \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o c\u1ea3\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/sergio-ramos-nhan-barca-khong-co-le-don-tan-vuong-nao-ca.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{cle