\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos nhan Barca se khong co le chao don nao ca.\" title=\"Sergio Ramos nh\u1eafn Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ec5 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/sergio-ramos-nhan-barca-khong-co-le-don-tan-vuong-nao-ca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sergio Ramos nh\u1eafn Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ec5 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n n\u00e0o c\u1ea3.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Real Madrid m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Juventus \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-0. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n HLV Zidane c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng La Liga n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ec5 tho\u00e1i v\u1ecb</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Barca, tr\u1eadn El Clasico di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/5 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Nou Camp ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid n\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u00e0 &quot;t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot; Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Real Madrid \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/sergio-ramos-44967.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Sergio Ramos</span></span> nh\u1eafn Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ec5 \u0111\u00f3n n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Nou Camp: &quot;V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Atletico&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Th\u1eadt bu\u1ed3n khi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga \u0111\u00e3 xa t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c c\u1ed5ng ch\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 \u01b0? Xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ed5ng ch\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;S\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ph\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5ng ch\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Barcelona quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1ng c\u1ed5ng ch\u00e0o danh d\u1ef1 ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ecd&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-Madrid.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Atletico Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Real Madrid 1-1 Barcelona:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/8/real-1-1-atletico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"931","checkdouble":"183842"},{"date":"07:04 09/04","title":"Atletico h\u00f2a Real Madrid, Diego Simeone g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111e d\u1ecda Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/9/atletico-hoa-real-madrid-diego-simeone-gui-loi-de-doa-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}