ty=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u1ec3 West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o Top 4 c\u1ee7a The Blues tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t mong manh.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i quen thu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 Premier League. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 2002 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, tr\u1ea3i qua 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, The Blues kh\u00f4ng thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 8 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. D\u00f9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Chelsea vs West Ham Top 4 xa dan roi hinh anh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Chelsea vs West Ham Top 4 xa d\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Du-am-Chelsea-vs-West-Ham-Top-4-xa-dan-roi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chelsea lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n West Ham, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang v\u1eadt \u1edf n\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. &ldquo;B\u00faa t\u1ea1&rdquo; v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi David Moyes h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1eafng hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, West Ham c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ec7 khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch. 4 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1eafng tay, nh\u1eadn h\u01a1n 3 b\u00e0n thua/tr\u1eadn. Xem ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea tr\u00fat gi\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng. B\u00f3ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn ch\u1ec9 l\u0103n tr\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Joe Hart li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trao \u0111\u1ea3o sau nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard, Willian hay Alvaro Morata.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea hoa 1-1 West Ham\" title=\"Chelsea hoa 1-1 West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/chelsea-bi-west-ham-cam-hoa-dieu-toi-te-nhat-con-chua-den.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nS\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi Morata ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Azpilicueta m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 phung ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Hazard hay Alonso \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. B\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Ph\u00fat 70, HLV David Moyes c\u1ee7a West Ham tung Chicharito v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, ch\u1ec9 3 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea </strong></span>t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Giroud v\u00e0 Pedro c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 xoay chuy\u1ec3n t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Conte cua Chelsea\" title=\"HLV Conte cua Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/HLV-Conte-cua-Chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf Premier League l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 12, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 v\u00e0 NHM c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n90 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 23 l\u1ea7n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 West Ham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 4 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Conte kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng r\u1eddi xa cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Top 4</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-chelsea-vs-west-ham-tran-dau-vong-33-premier-league-201718-172-183823.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng r\u1eddi xa cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Top 4. V\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi West Ham, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 m\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ebfn 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea da bi Top 4 bo xa den 10 diem\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Top 4 b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ebfn 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Top 4 b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ebfn 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u m\u1edbi gi\u00fap Chelsea san b\u1eb1ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, 14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u1ecd thua t\u1edbi 7 tr\u1eadn. \u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t The Blues ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n tr\u1eafng tay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roman Abramovich c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn c\u1ee7a t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Conte \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Chelsea vs West Ham\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Chelsea-vs-West-Ham.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-chelsea-11-west-ham-172-183837.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Chelsea 1-1 West Ham<br>\r\n</strong></span><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"927","checkdouble":"183840"},{"date":"06:03 09/04","title":"T\u1ea1o n\u00ean 2 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, Jack Wilshere b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/tao-nen-2-the-do-jack-wilshere-bi-chi-trich-du-doi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full