pacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 2 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa Arsenal vs Southampton.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 64 thay cho Reiss Nelson, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/jack-wilshere-43841.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Jack Wilshere</span></span> kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn Wilshere l\u00e0 pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Jack Stephens b\u00ean ph\u00eda Southampton, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang \u0111\u1ebfn hai th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere bi chi trich vi khien tran cau nong hon muc can thiet.\" title=\"Wilshere b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/tao-nen-2-the-do-jack-wilshere-bi-chi-trich-du-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Wilshere b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, Arsenal c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Wilshere \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh x\u1ea5u x\u00ed khi ch\u1ea1y theo k\u00e9o \u00e1o Jack Stephens khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Southampton t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn, d\u1eabn t\u1edbi pha t\u00f3m c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Wilshere \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Stephens \u0111\u00e3 sai v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi k\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0ng Wilshere c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00fang. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh k\u00e9o r\u00e1ch c\u1ea3 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, Stephens sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n Wilshere ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Mohames Elneny ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0nh vi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p khi\u1ebfn Jack Wilshere b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i, HLV Mark Hughes cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. N\u1ebfu Stephens b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i, Wilshere c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh khi Wilshere l\u00ean g\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Stephens. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilshere \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf Arsenal c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110T Anh. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Frank Lampard cho r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>, Jack Wilshere ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal vs Southampton\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Southampton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Arsenal-vs-Southampton.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Southampton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Arsenal 3-2 Southampton:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\