height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng West Ham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Antonio Conte ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cesar-azpilicueta-44360.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Cesar Azpilicueta</span></span>, Chelsea l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn ba \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham. S\u1ef1 l\u01a1i l\u1ecfng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn The Blues ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte chi ra van de cua Chelsea khien ho that bai trong mua nay.\" title=\"Antonio Conte ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/antonio-conte-chi-ra-van-de-cua-chelsea-sau-tran-hoa-west-ham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Antonio Conte ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChicharito ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1i duy\u00ean khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u1edbi pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u1edbi top 4 trong BXH Premier League l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 5 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/antonio-conte-147.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Antonio Conte</span></span> k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea: &quot;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh cho c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00e3 bao nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n t\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ed3i?&quot;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Sau \u0111\u00f3, West Ham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua ngay m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n. Chelsea ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, mong r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho v\u1eadn may, ch\u00fang ta ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 g\u00ec t\u00edch c\u1ef1c&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, HLV David Moyes cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Nh\u00ecn chung h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t. Chicharito l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Chelsea vs West Ham\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Chelsea-vs-West-Ham.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs West Ham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p Chelsea 1-1 West Ham:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265880\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n   