:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Chelsea vs West Ham tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 33 gi\u1ea3i Premier League 2017/18 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u derby th\u00e0nh London Chelsea vs West Ham v\u00f2ng 33 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2017/18 l\u00fac 22h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 8/4.</h2>\r\n<p>Chelsea \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/eden-hazard-44350.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard</span> \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa  s\u00e2n r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc West Ham. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c  c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 West Ham kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n  c\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian la cai ten choi noi bat trong hiep mot tran Chelsea vs West Ham.\" title=\"Willian l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/willian.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Willian l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br>\r\nD\u00f9 t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Chelsea l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1  nguy hi\u1ec3m. Ph\u00fat 21, Willian d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m ng\u01b0\u1eddi Cresswell \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng  kh\u00f4ng \u0111i v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh. Willian l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda  khung th\u00e0nh West Ham h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 pha c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111i  ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc \u1edf ph\u00fat 31.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 36, Willian c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Joe Hart. Ngay sau  \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cesar-azpilicueta-44360.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cesar Azpilicueta</span> tho\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m  tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Joe Hart ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft  \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn.</p>\r\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, West Ham c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3  t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m. K\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 West Ham,  t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Antonio Conte.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-chelsea-vs-west-ham-22h30-ngay-84-premier-league-201718-372-183811.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/ket-qua-chelsea-vs-west-ham-tran-dau-vong-33-premier-league-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-chelsea-vs-west-ham-22h30-ngay-84-premier-league-201718-372-183811.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Chelsea 1-0 West Ham (H1): Azpilicueta \u0111\u01b0a The Blues v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chelsea vs West Ham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u derby th\u00e0nh London Chelsea vs West Ham...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br>\r\n<strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></p>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"924","checkdouble":"183823"},{"date":"22:38 08/04","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Real Madrid vs Atletico tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 31 La Liga 2017/18","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/ket-qua-real-madrid-vs-atletico-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-vid