g phong. Trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Southampton, HLV Wenger ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung diem nhan sau tran Arsenal vs Southampton hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Southampton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Nhung-diem-nhan-sau-tran-Arsenal-vs-Southampton-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aubameyang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n kh\u00e9o c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Aubameyang ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 cho Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh McCarthy k\u1ecbp b\u0103ng ra.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAubameyang \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League (6 b\u00e0n c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o), anh \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Danny Welbeck</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton, HLV Wenger \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/daniel-welbeck-43819.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Danny Welbeck</strong></span>, anh ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111e d\u1ecda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9.&nbsp;Welbeck g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck mang ve chien thang cho Arsenal\" title=\"Welbeck mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/welbeck.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Welbeck mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Aubameyang g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1. Khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Welbeck \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ebfn nay th\u00ec Welbeck m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League, NHM Arsenal \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Southampton kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3. Khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn 14 l\u1ea7n, 8 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng. C\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech va cac dong doi noi hang thu co mot ngay thi dau that vong\" title=\"Cech v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/cech.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cech v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Cech v\u00e0 Mustafi, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1ea5t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Shane Long nhanh ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Chambers m\u1eafc m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Cedric c\u0103ng ngang gi\u00fap Austin g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn gi\u00fap Arsenal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1i duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Shane Long kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Southampton c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shane Long r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 duy\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u1edf Premier League, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t nhanh sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u00fd gi\u1eefa th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Mustafi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shane Long khong the giup Southampton co diem\" title=\"Shane Long kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Southampton c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/222451-long.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shane Long kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Southampton c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nShane Long \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Arsenal \u1edf Premier League, ch\u1ec9 Aston Villa (6) l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. Nh\u01b0ng pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Long kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Southampton tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn thua 2-3, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eafng tay r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 Southampton d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 3-2. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-arsenal-vs-southampton-tran-dau-vong-33-ngoai-hang-anh-201718-172-183820.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Southampton</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Ri\u00eang \u1edf Premier League h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi 8 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 2 b\u00e0n thua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal thang tran thu 6 tren moi mat tran\" title=\"Arsenal th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/arsenal.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nArsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong 23 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 17 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u1ebfn nay Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Arsenal </strong></span>\u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Top 4 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m, d\u00f9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CSKA Moskva trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Southampton r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Southampton \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Emirates, h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. Tuy nhi\u00ean, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a Welbeck khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch tr\u1eafng tay ra v\u1ec1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp Southampton kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 18 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mark Hughes con rat nhieu viec phai lam neu muon giup Southampton tru hang thanh cong\" title=\"Mark Hughes c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Southampton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/huge.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mark Hughes c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Southampton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m an to\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Southampton ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng xa v\u1eddi. HLV Mark Hughes v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Southampton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Southampton<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Arsenal vs Southampton\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Southampton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Arsenal-vs-Southampton.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal vs Southampton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video Arsenal 3-2 Southampton (V\u00f2ng 33 Premier League 2017/18)<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265857\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-arsenal-vs-southampton-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscr