\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Petr Cech.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shane Long mo ty so tran dau\" title=\"Shane Long m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/long.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Shane Long m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nPh\u00fat 17, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. Shane Long t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu \u0103n \u00fd gi\u1eefa Cech v\u00e0 Mustafi \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. B\u00e0n thua \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh, h\u1ecd t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb ph\u00fat 29 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 38, Aubameyang v\u00e0 Welbeck ghi li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-1. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aubameyang va Welbeck giup Arsenal vuot len dan truoc 2-1\" title=\"Aubameyang v\u00e0 Welbeck gi\u00fap Arsenal v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/auba.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Aubameyang v\u00e0 Welbeck gi\u00fap Arsenal v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Arsenal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ph\u00fat 53, Iwobi tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh McCarthy \u0111\u00e3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. Sau \u0111\u00f3 2 ph\u00fat Southampton c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ef1c c\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Hojbjerg, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.</p>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>ARSENAL:</strong> Cech, Bellerin, Chambers, Mustafi, Kolasinac, Elneny, Xhaka, Iwobi, Nelson, Welbeck, Aubameyang.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 b\u1ecb: </strong>Lacazette, Wilshere, Ozil, Holding, Monreal, Macey, Nketiah.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>SOUTHAMPTON:</strong> McCarthy, Cedric, Stephens, Hoedt, Yoshida, Bertrand, Ward-Prowse, Hojbjerg, Romeu, Tadic, Long.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 b\u1ecb: </strong>Austin, Boufal, Gabbiadini, Redmond, Pied, Sims, Forster</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"919","checkdouble":"183820"},{"date":"10:25 08/04","title":"L\u1eafp bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Vinh b\u1ecb ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/lap-bien-quang-cao-dien-tu-doi-bong-cua-cong-vinh-bi-che-trach.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height