d9i 5-0 HAGL</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 d\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vui m\u1eebng khi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay l\u00e0 Duy M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111au sau nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chan thuong cua Duy Manh phai nghi thi dau bao lau hinh anh\" title=\"Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u bao l\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/chan-thuong-cua-duy-manh-phai-nghi-thi-dau-bao-lau.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 1 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/tranh-cai-quanh-viec-bau-duc-phat-tang-tien-vi-dap-vao-chan-duy-manh-291-183617.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u00ean ph\u00eda HAGL</span>. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i sau \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn ph\u1ea3i ch\u01b0\u1eddm \u0111\u00e1. R\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 sau khi \u0111i ch\u1ee5p t\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n, c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Duy M\u1ea1nh b\u1ecb ph\u1ed3ng r\u1ed9p c\u01a1, ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kho\u1ea3ng 1 tu\u1ea7n.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh, Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kho\u1ea3ng hai tu\u1ea7n. Trung v\u1ec7 20 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb c\u0103ng c\u01a1 h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u00e3n c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f9i sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario b\u00ean ph\u00eda HAGL. \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 Duy M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lo l\u1eafng. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c kho\u1ea3ng 70-80% nh\u01b0ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft hay Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eafc L\u1eafc t\u1ea1i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 18h00 (9/4) tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duy-manh-len-tieng-sau-pha-bong-triet-ha-cua-cau-thu-hagl-168-183604.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/duy-manh-len-tieng-sau-pha-bong-triet-ha-cua-cau-thu-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/duy-manh-len-tieng-sau-pha-bong-triet-ha-cua-cau-thu-hagl-168-183604.html\">Duy M\u1ea1nh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau pha b\u00f3ng tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n trong pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 HAGL, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mong c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"917","checkdouble":"183804"},{"date":"19:59 08/04","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 08/04: Pogba s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 Neymar?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/8/diem-tin-toi-0804-pogba-sap-doi-cho-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adCon